    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Develop Your Product\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you refine and enhance your final product that showcases your future prediction.\r\n\r\nYou can share examples, upload images or documents, and give feedback on AI’s responses to improve the result.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to:\r\n    - Improve the content, structure, or tone of your final product\r\n    - Generate supporting text, dialogue, visuals, or other elements for your chosen format\r\n    - Make your message clearer, more engaging, and tailored to your audience\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Tips for Better Results**\r\n- Be specific about your format and audience (e.g., “Write this for a 6th grade audience in the style of a speech”)\r\n- Ask AI to revise for clarity, tone, or voice\r\n- Don’t just accept AI’s first draft—revise and guide it to reflect your ideas\r\n\r\n",
